episodes.title: School of Philosophy - Ch4 report into Child Abuse at their school, St James's UK - Pt 2
episodes.description:
The SES (School of Economic Science) was founded in the 1930's. By the 1960's Philosophy was introduced and they created the School of Philosophy, an offshoot of the SES.

This School currently offer classes in Practical Philosophy in over 16 countries. In Ireland their base in on the Northumberland Rd in south Dublin.

They claim they are the School of Philosophy but this is misleading, they are a School of A Philosophy; their own.

This warrants more investigation. If you are thinking of attending their classes or know of anyone involved, you can find more information at these links:

Belgian Government Report into teh School:

http://www.whyaretheydead.net/misc/SES/english.html

Website dealing with the investigation contained within this report:

http://www.stjamesinquiry.org/index.html
subjects: School of Philosophy and Economic Science
